text: Saif Ali Khan (born 16 August 1970) is an Indian actor.Biography at imdb.com He was born to Sharmila Tagore, great-grandniece of Rabindranath Tagore. In January 2025, Khan was hospitalized in Mumbai after being stabbed multiple times during a home invasion. == References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Indian actors
